Package: ggcleveland
Title: Implementation of plots from Cleveland's Visualizing Data book in ggplot2
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Marcos",
         family = "Prunello",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "marcosprunello@gmail.com",
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9611-527X")
         ),
  person(given = "Gonzalo",
         family = "Mari",
         role = c("aut")
         )
  )
Description: This packages provides functions to produce ggplot versions for 
	some visualizations tools described in Cleveland's book "Visualizing Data". This
	package is experimental and was thought to be used in the context of a course on 
	exploratory data analysis. Any contributions or feedback are appreciated. Note
	that this package does not create any new stats or geom layers.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
